(1992, 69, '10 National income help in the comparisons of the changes in the components of the economy over time and across the frontiers are made impossible only by the estimates in the national income accounts.', 'TRUE', 'FALSE', 'Not sure', 'none of the above', 'B', '2016-02-18 00:04:38'),
