(2020, 69, '18 Developing countries stand to gain from international trade because', 'Trade enables them to specialize in producing where they have a comparative advantage', 'Trade gives them access to the greater variety of goods produced abroad', 'Trade subjects their local producers to greater competition', 'All of the above', 'D', '2016-02-18 00:04:38'),
