(2483, 15, '19 Which pair is not an organ of African Unity?', 'The Assembly of Heads of state and the Excutive Concil', 'Specialised committees and Pan-African parliament', 'Court of hustice and Economics and social Council etc', 'World Health Organisation and European Commission', 'D', '2016-04-11 21:18:27'),
(2484, 15, '20 Which pair is not a method of peaceful settlement of dispute?', 'Concillation and Mediation', 'Arbitration and Judicial method', 'Concillation and Arbtitration', 'Reprisal and Intervention', 'D', '2016-04-11 21:18:27'),
