e administration of our foundation has attempted to make us crazy graduates, however we decline to be insane. Just crazy graduates fit in with negativities and acknowledge shamefulness to endeavor without addressing, we can?t be insane; we decline to fit in with the infringement of our rights. \r\nIt is additionally relevant to express that, while the University ought to be glad for its understudies for remaining for truth and equity, it is caught up with attempting to criminalize us. \r\nOn the 28th October, 2015, administration of our establishment flowed a reminder to all study focuses, illuminating the chiefs to restriction understudies from having any social occasion. In this reminder, they rehashed the bogus case of risk to life of the Vice Chancellor after it had been legitimately cleared to be false at the police base camp. \r\nIt turned out to be clear to all that, the administration realizes that the presence of Student Association will deaden heap of inconsistencies from which the administration in no time advantages; thus, their push to deny understudies their rights. \r\nWhile they had reliably neglected to get our law graduates to be prepared for graduate school following 2013, neglected to get our graduates activated for NYSC in spite of accepting expenses in such manner, they are energetically attempting endeavors to disabled person equity to support them. \r\nThis lethargic demeanor, coercion and blatant infringement of understudy rights had incited the whole understudies of the foundation over the alliance so much that the require an across the nation dissent had achieved its definitive high. \r\nIn perspective of this, it is important to express that, this is a time of progress, and this change won''t leave without visiting NOUN. \r\nTo keep away from violate down of lawfulness in the establishment, we along these lines approach President Muhammadu Buhari to quickly sack the accompanying: \r\nThe Vice Chancellor (Professor Vincent Ado Tenebe). \r\